originalText.text: Dr. Kyle Warner is helpful, thorough, personable, proactive, dedicated, knowledgeable and a good listener!!! I made excellent progress because of his help!!! Check out Yupo Health, which also has a superior Acupuncturist and Herbalist, Ching Po (Eva) Huang!!! The Massage Therapists and Receptionists are helpful, too!!!
